N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 296-1.2 - Rules applicable

State Regulations

All of the rules in this Subchapter and all of the
rules in Subchapter A of Chapter IV of this Subtitle that pertain to vehicle
parking, are applicable to State employees parking in OGS paid parking
facilities managed by the Bureau of Parking Services. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9
§§
296-1.2

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
